snippet.title: NightmareZ Official Trailer Indie Game
snippet.description:
Buy NightmareZ on my website(DRM-Free + Steam Key): http://www.amaxang-games.com/2015/04/nightmarez-full-version-indie-roguelike.html
Or,
Buy NightmareZ on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/509930

NightmareZ is a side-scrolling platform action game with lots of fancy features, many enemies and retro visuals.
